<br>
He doesn't dispell, and his AOE is a DoT (not a DD) that's dispellable...it's pretty obvious (at least after the first fight) how to best counteract this.<br>
<br>
His Fear is pretty bad too if you don't have a lot of high level folks with decent MR gear, but in all he's a pretty straight up fight--melees burn /discs after resisting a fear, send nukers in after the melees have a bit of aggro going.  And fighting him near the Burning Woods zoneline makes for a fairly stable fight environment (i.e., you won't get many adds from folks running off if you fight him near that little crest of a hill).<br>
<br>
Kattibrie Puppypaws<br>
Heirophant of Kabald<br>
The Seventh Hammer<br>
